<a data-tip="p$t$lisongwei" href="/people/lisongwei">李松蔚</a>，<strong title="欢迎关注微信公众号：therapistlsw" class="zu-question-my-bio">欢迎关注微信公众号：therapistlsw</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="19">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yu-wa-wa-27" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yu-wa-wa-27" class="zg-link" title="柒文硕">柒文硕</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$qing-jiu-jiu-97" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/qing-jiu-jiu-97" class="zg-link" title="卿九九">卿九九</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhang-shuai-19-68" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhang-shuai-19-68" class="zg-link" title="张帅">张帅</a></span>
